{"tid":948433,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"屌那星！我發現HR部門真係全公司最撚狗既部門","createTime":"2018-12-20T05:18:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T07:32:59.000Z","uid":192815,"like":285,"dislike":87,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"ba15ffc957fb8cf5608d19bd48f61b2cd5701ebe","tid":948433,"uid":192815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T05:18:27.000Z","msg":"話說最近見工，有一間center已經想請我，之後彈左我份資料去HR<br />\n<br />\n個HR阿姐打黎要求多多，煩過閪咁<br />\n<br />\n第一：朋友做咨詢人唔得（如果之前無返過工要填邊個？）<br />\n第二：要晒Asso and Degree transcript（屌啦星，畢左業咁耐真係無申請過，加上之前幾份工請我都無要求過要transcript）<br />\n第三：問我返pt拎工作證明（炒散呀姐姐，炒散點撚樣有工作證明比你呀屌那星，係咪未撚炒過散？）<br />\n第四：打黎壓價（屌，係center已經比人壓完2000，你打黎再壓？）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有太多不能盡錄<br />\n<br />\n想問下咁多位爸打係咪HR都係要狗先做得？"},{"pid":"5dea875018195280567af0c67925ff13cbbad902","tid":948433,"uid":19141,"like":171,"dislike":6,"score":165,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T05:20:37.000Z","msg":"慘得過你比狗撚"},{"pid":"b2eccc87766b15f756a80584c06b271a5f7a21fe","tid":948433,"uid":122118,"like":87,"dislike":110,"score":-23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T05:23:44.000Z","msg":"發覺真係好多後門狗讀大學"},{"pid":"95228aaf5ac541fe785ddbea5a5078637855de77","tid":948433,"uid":189507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T05:23:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b341d582940977d60655f3ddab3cdda0eeb96956","tid":948433,"uid":34411,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T05:28:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88ca7e463e53319406c8f78e511a2d77be8be71c","tid":948433,"uid":7343,"like":54,"dislike":2,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T05:31:31.000Z","msg":"HR富貴階層就係未撚炒過散"},{"pid":"f8feccc5835ea546de78098b3b07aa1bb9957596","tid":948433,"uid":192815,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88ca7e463e53319406c8f78e511a2d77be8be71c","tid":948433,"uid":7343,"like":54,"dislike":2,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T05:31:31.000Z","msg":"HR富貴階層就係未撚炒過散"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T05:55:02.000Z","msg":"HR搵好多？"},{"pid":"588e2