,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T00:00:20.000Z","msg":"D HR最on9就係唔熟行程，但又會同個部門主管一齊in人果陣扮熟，問埋d廢問題，屌佢老味HR好心就處理下文件咪算囉，難怪做親多數係女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5cf3814cbf786fa6d9001790b2eccb6fa077507","tid":948433,"uid":48085,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T00:16:20.000Z","msg":"抄散同Pt都未識分？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n抄一世散算啦垃圾樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef7ffdeb2fd67fda4d577bed45d5edce1d3b784","tid":948433,"uid":29093,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T00:23:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小朋友， 1, 2, 3 其實算合理要求嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"955a5faf053b8db6fc593f8d0ea3e63773054779","tid":948433,"uid":29093,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cef7ffdeb2fd67fda4d577bed45d5edce1d3b784","tid":948433,"uid":29093,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T00:23:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小朋友， 1, 2, 3 其實算合理要求嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T00:26:32.000Z","msg":"無證明之下， 1,2,3 任鳩你吹啦 <br />\n兒登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72709360538f65037f980c7cfaed3ef5c699ace6","tid":948433,"uid":29093,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"97996ae21e90b91390bdab93072b0a957f339e2c","tid":948433,"uid":55533,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T08:45:19.000Z","msg":"專科grad?<br />\n拎transcript好正常喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T00:28:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關咩事 ,  畀人地了解你讀過乜， 好正常下話"},{"pid":"c93